{
  "texts": [
    "We then use the cosine similarity metric to identify how semantically similar the new problem is to existing problems.",
    "To demonstrate how syntactic and semantic textual similarity can be used, we generate several new instances of maintenance problems.",
    "The first new problem is almost identical to a consistently appearing existing maintenance problem in the MWOs.",
    "The second maintenance problem is also identical, but only semantically.",
    "The third maintenance problem shows how close semantic and syntactic matches can be obtained if similar words appear in both pieces of text."
  ]
}